## Usage Patterns

### Basic Usage

```tsx
() => {
  return (
    <AppTile
      label="Home"
      icon={<Home />}
      product="intuit"
      onClick={action('Clicked tile')}
    />
  );
}
```

### Quickbooks Tile

```tsx
() => {
  return (
    <AppTile
      label="Sales & Payments"
      icon={<Quickbooks />}
      product="quickbooks"
      onClick={action('Clicked tile')}
    />
  );
}
```

### Multi Theme Tiles

```tsx
() => {
  return (
    <div className={styles.tilesList}>
      <AppTile label="Home" icon={<Home />} />
      <AppTile label="Customers" icon={<Mailchimp />} product="mailchimp" />
      <AppTile
        label="Sales & Payments"
        icon={<Quickbooks />}
        product="quickbooks"
      />
      <AppTile
        label="Bills & Expenses"
        icon={<Quickbooks />}
        product="quickbooks"
      />
      <AppTile label="Bookkeeping" icon={<Quickbooks />} product="quickbooks" />
      <AppTile
        label="Lending & Banking"
        icon={<Quickbooks />}
        product="quickbooks"
      />
    </div>
  );
}
```

### Recommendations

```tsx
() => {
  return (
    <div className={styles.tilesList}>
      <AppTile
        recommendation
        label="Payroll & HR"
        icon={<Quickbooks />}
        product="quickbooks"
      />
      <AppTile
        recommendation
        label="Business Tax"
        icon={<Turbotax />}
        product="turbotax"
      />
      <AppTile
        recommendation
        label="Marketing"
        icon={<Mailchimp />}
        product="mailchimp"
      />
    </div>
  );
}
```

